snippet.title: 9Th Update part 1
snippet.description:
This is the 9Th trailer (movie) of my newest HL2 ep2 sp-mod, called Episode 3, ("The Closure"). It shows gameplay fotage of the last 3 new maps that i made over the last few months. Should you want to see all other movies and or douzens of screenshots then please go to my Ep3 TC Moddb site here;

http://www.moddb.com/mods/episode-3-the-closure
